      "post_content": "[Pernicious Deed](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pernicious Deed) is much closer to a board clearing spell like [Wrath of God](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wrath of God) or [Planer Cleansing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Planer Cleansing). [Punishment](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Punishment) is more like a spot removal spell like [Vindicate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vindicate) or [Maelstrom Pulse](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Maelstrom Pulse), like a7141988 mentioned. This card seems to be inspired by Deed, but is less powerful to offset the option of casting Crime instead.",
